             were indicted for <rs id="t18290611-141-off736" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290611-141-off736" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-141-off736" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290611-141-cd737" type="crimeDate">2d of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-141-off736 t18290611-141-cd737"></join>, 76 lbs. weight of lead, value 12s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290611-141-victim1080" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Cleave
                        <interp inst="t18290611-141-victim1080" type="surname" value="Cleave"></interp>
